(9,1,'2023-09-16 11:33:07','2023-09-16 11:33:07','<div style=\"padding: 10px;\">\r\n\r\nm Ging Sinh (hay m vng l Noel) bt u t chiu ti ngy 24/12. Vo m Noel, mi ngi quy qun bn nhau v ng gi Noel s i pht qu\r\n\r\n<a href=\"https://giangsinh.vn\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">L Ging Sinh</a> hay cn gi l l Thin Cha ging sinh l dp k nim ngy Cha Jesus c sinh ra, l mt trong nhng ngy l ln thng 12 hng nm. L Ging Sinh din ra vo 24 v 25/12.\r\n\r\nL Ging Sinh rt  ngha v quan trng vi ngi theo o Thin Cha. Vo ngy ny nhiu gia nh thng <a href=\"https://mona.vn/trang-tri-giang-sinh/phu-kien-trang-tri-cay-thong-noel/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">trang tr cy thng noel</a>, tng cha, rt p. y cng l dp  mi ngi trong gia nh quy qun bn nhau, n nhng mn n mang khng kh Noel.\r\n<h3 id=\"hmenuid1\" class=\"wp-block-heading\">1m Ging Sinh l ngy no?</h3>\r\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img class=\"wp-image-34482\" src=\"https://mona.vn/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/dem-giang-sinh-la-ngay-nao-phan-biet-dem-24-va-ngay-25-12-202211140652087357.jpg\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" srcset=\"https://mona.vn/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/dem-giang-sinh-la-ngay-nao-phan-biet-dem-24-va-ngay-25-12-202211140652087357.jpg 800w, https://mona.vn/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/dem-giang-sinh-la-ngay-nao-phan-biet-dem-24-va-ngay-25-12-202211140652087357-768x432.jpg 768w\" alt=\"\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" /></figure>\r\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center\"><em>m Ging Sinh l ngy no?</em></p>\r\nGing nh hng nm, theo dng lch th L Ging Sinh nm ny s din ra vo ti 24/12 v ht ngy 25/12.<strong>Theo ngi Do Thi th ngy mi s bt u t lc hong hn, v th h t chc l Ging Sinh sm t ti ngy 24. Cn ngy 25/12 l ngy lm l chnh thc.</strong>\r\n<h3 id=\"hmenuid2\" class=\"wp-block-heading\">2S khc nhau gia m 24/12 v ngy 25/12</h3>\r\n<h4 id=\"1hchildmenuid1\" class=\"wp-block-heading\"><strong>m Ging Sinh 24/12  l vng</strong></h4>\r\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img class=\"wp-image-34481\" src=\"https://mona.vn/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/dem-giang-sinh-la-ngay-nao-phan-biet-dem-24-va-ngay-25-12-202211140652451406.jpg\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" srcset=\"https://mona.vn/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/dem-giang-sinh-la-ngay-nao-phan-biet-dem-24-va-ngay-25-12-202211140652451406.jpg 800w, https://mona.vn/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/dem-giang-sinh-la-ngay-nao-phan-biet-dem-24-va-ngay-25-12-202211140652451406-768x432.jpg 768w\" alt=\"\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" /></figure>\r\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center\"><em>m Ging Sinh 24/12  l vng</em></p>\r\nTheo Cng gio Roma, m 24/12 l thi im l vng. Vo thi gian ny  thnh ng v trong nh u trang tr nhng hnh nh v biu tng ca l Ging Sinh nh cy thng noel, hang  tng c M Maria, tng Ba Vua, mt s thin thn,\r\n\r\nm 24/12 cn l s ra i ca <a href=\"https://phukiengiangsinh.vn/cay-thong-noel/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">cy thng Noel</a>. Vo cui th k th VII Thnh Boniface  ang trn ng hnh hng th gp mt nhm ngi dng mt a b  cng t cy si. ng  dng mt qu m h gc cy si  gii cu a b.<strong>Ti ni ny  mc ln mt cy thng nh, Thnh Boniface  ni vi mi ngi rng, cy thng ny l cy ca s sng v tng trng cho cuc sng vnh hng ca Cha. T  cy thng tr thnh biu tng trong ngy l Noel, l biu tng ca sc sng mi v nhng nim hy vng.</strong>\r\n<h4 id=\"1hchildmenuid2\" class=\"wp-block-heading\"><strong>Ngy Ging Sinh 25/12  l chnh ngy</strong></h4>\r\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img class=\"wp-image-34480\" src=\"https://mona.vn/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/dem-giang-sinh-la-ngay-nao-phan-biet-dem-24-va-ngay-25-12-202211140652333069.jpg\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" srcset=\"https://mona.vn/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/dem-giang-sinh-la-ngay-nao-phan-biet-dem-24-va-ngay-25-12-202211140652333069.jpg 800w, https://mona.vn/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/dem-giang-sinh-la-ngay-nao-phan-biet-dem-24-va-ngay-25-12-202211140652333069-768x432.jpg 768w\" alt=\"\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" /></figure>\r\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center\"><em>Ngy Ging Sinh 25/12  l chnh ngy</em></p>\r\nNhiu ngi ngh rng, 25/12 l ngy sinh chnh thc ca ngy Cha Jesus, tuy nhin y l iu khng chnh xc v cha c ti liu no khng nh. Chng ta ch bit Cha Jesus sinh ra trong mt chung gia sc vo mt m ma ng lnh.\r\n\r\nT , cc tn  C c  t chc n mng.<strong>Tuy nhin trc s cm on ca chnh quyn La M, h  b mt chn ngy 25/12  t chc. Ngy ny cn l ngy trng vi l Thn Mt Tri ca ngi La M.</strong>\r\n\r\nn nm 312 Hong  La M Constantine I  b thn gio theo C c gio v hu b l Thn Mt Tri. T , ngy 25/12 tr thnh ngy l mng sinh nht ca Cha Jesus hng nm.<strong>n nm 354 Gio hong Libero mi chnh thc cng b 25/12 l ngy c hnh l Ging Sinh hay gi l L Noel.</strong>\r\n<h3 id=\"hmenuid3\" class=\"wp-block-heading\">3 ngha ca m Noel</h3>\r\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img class=\"wp-image-34479\" src=\"https://mona.vn/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/dem-giang-sinh-la-ngay-nao-phan-biet-dem-24-va-ngay-25-12-202211140652208914.jpg\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" srcset=\"https://mona.vn/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/dem-giang-sinh-la-ngay-nao-phan-biet-dem-24-va-ngay-25-12-202211140652208914.jpg 800w, https://mona.vn/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/dem-giang-sinh-la-ngay-nao-phan-biet-dem-24-va-ngay-25-12-202211140652208914-768x432.jpg 768w\" alt=\"\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" /></figure>\r\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center\"><em> ngha ca m Noel</em></p>\r\nm Noel ngoi  ngha theo o Thin Cha th cn l mt m c quyn  mi ngi trong gia nh quy qun bn nhau, n chung mt ba n, mt m khng ng  nghe nhng cu chuyn c thut li bn cy thng Noel.\r\n\r\nm Noel cng l mt bui l ca nhng a tr, mt m thn diu m tt c iu c ca cc b iu thnh s tht.\r\n\r\nNgy Noel cng l mt thng ip ca ho bnh: Vinh danh Thng  trn cao  Bnh an cho ngi di th ,<strong>y l cu c ht bi nhng thin thn bo tin s xut hin ca v cu th v Noel cng l ngy ngi ta chia s vi nhng ai b b ri, b c n, bnh hon, gi yu</strong>\r\n<h3 id=\"hmenuid4\" class=\"wp-block-heading\">4Cc hot ng trong m Noel 24/12</h3>\r\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img class=\"wp-image-34478\" src=\"https://mona.vn/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/dem-giang-sinh-la-ngay-nao-phan-biet-dem-24-va-ngay-25-12-202211140653002505.jpg\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" srcset=\"https://mona.vn/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/dem-giang-sinh-la-ngay-nao-phan-biet-dem-24-va-ngay-25-12-202211140653002505.jpg 800w, https://mona.vn/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/dem-giang-sinh-la-ngay-nao-phan-biet-dem-24-va-ngay-25-12-202211140653002505-768x432.jpg 768w\" alt=\"\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" /></figure>\r\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center\"><em>Trang tr cy thng Noel ti nh</em></p>\r\nTrong dp Noel th <a href=\"https://mona.vn/trang-tri-giang-sinh/cay-thong-noel/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">cy thng ging sinh</a> l biu tng khng th thiu, y l mt trong nhng hot ng vui v, m p. C nh quy qun bn nhau cng trang tr cy thng Noel tht m cng.\r\n\r\nTu mi nh m cy thng Noel c trang tr khc nhau, thng thy l nhng chic chung, tt, qu cu, hp qu,\r\n<h4 id=\"3hchildmenuid2\" class=\"wp-block-heading\"><strong>ng gi Noel tng qu</strong></h4>\r\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img class=\"wp-image-34477\" src=\"https://mona.vn/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/dem-giang-sinh-la-ngay-nao-phan-biet-dem-24-va-ngay-25-12-202211140653132581.jpg\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" srcset=\"https://mona.vn/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/dem-giang-sinh-la-ngay-nao-phan-biet-dem-24-va-ngay-25-12-202211140653132581.jpg 800w, https://mona.vn/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/dem-giang-sinh-la-ngay-nao-phan-biet-dem-24-va-ngay-25-12-202211140653132581-768x432.jpg 768w\" alt=\"\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" /></figure>\r\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center\"><em>ng gi Noel tng qu cho cc b</em></p>\r\nHnh nhng gi Noeltng qu khng th thiu trong dp l Noel.<strong>ng gi Noel do con ngi ho trang, mang theo mt ti qu ln  tng cho cc em nh.</strong>y cng l hot ng m cc bn nh rt thch trong m Noel.\r\n<h4 id=\"3hchildmenuid3\" class=\"wp-block-heading\"><strong>T chc tic Ging sinh</strong></h4>\r\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img class=\"wp-image-34476\" src=\"https://mona.vn/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/dem-giang-sinh-la-ngay-nao-phan-biet-dem-24-va-ngay-25-12-202211140653279095.jpg\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" srcset=\"https://mona.vn/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/dem-giang-sinh-la-ngay-nao-phan-biet-dem-24-va-ngay-25-12-202211140653279095.jpg 800w, https://mona.vn/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/dem-giang-sinh-la-ngay-nao-phan-biet-dem-24-va-ngay-25-12-202211140653279095-768x432.jpg 768w\" alt=\"\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" /></figure>\r\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center\"><em>T chc tic Ging sinh ti nh</em></p>\r\nGing sinh cng l dp nhng ngi thn trong gia nh, bn b on t, hp mt bn nn khng th thiu mt bui tic nho nh.<strong>Vo thi tit se lnh ca nhng ngy cui nm, nhng ngi thn yu ngi quay qun bn nhau v cng thng thc nhng mn n ngon th tht m cng phi khng no.</strong>\r\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img class=\"wp-image-34475\" src=\"https://mona.vn/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/dem-giang-sinh-la-ngay-nao-phan-biet-dem-24-va-ngay-25-12-202211140653391616.jpg\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" srcset=\"https://mona.vn/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/dem-giang-sinh-la-ngay-nao-phan-biet-dem-24-va-ngay-25-12-202211140653391616.jpg 800w, https://mona.vn/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/dem-giang-sinh-la-ngay-nao-phan-biet-dem-24-va-ngay-25-12-202211140653391616-768x432.jpg 768w\" alt=\"\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" /></figure>\r\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center\"><em>Tng thip Ging sinh</em></p>\r\nVo m Noel ngi ta thng tng nhau cho nhau nhng tm thip mang y tnh yu thng, bn trong thip l nhng tm t mun gi gm, nhng li chc nhau. Ngoi ra thit k ca thip ngy nay rt p v a dng, cng lm tn thm  ngha ca mn qu.\r\n\r\n<em>Hy vng qua bi vit ny gip bn bit c m Ging Sinh l ngy no? Phn bit m 24/12 v ngy 25/12. Chc bn v gia nh c ma Ging Sinh vui v v m p.</em>\r\n\r\n</div>','m Ging Sinh l ngy no? Phn bit m 24 v ngy 25/12','','publish','open','open','','dem-giang-sinh-la-ngay-nao-phan-biet-dem-24-va-ngay-25-12','','','2023-09-16 13:27:48','2023-09-16 13:27:48','',0,'http://localhost/mona/?p=9',0,'post','',0),
