re>\r\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center\"><em>ng gi Noel tng qu cho cc b</em></p>\r\n<p>Hnh nh&nbsp;ng gi Noel&nbsp;tng qu khng th thiu trong dp l Noel.&nbsp;<strong>ng gi Noel do con ngi ho trang, mang theo mt ti qu ln  tng cho cc em nh.</strong>&nbsp;y cng l hot ng m cc bn nh rt thch trong m Noel.</p>\r\n<h4 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"3hchildmenuid3\"><strong>T chc tic Ging sinh</strong></h4>\r\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" src=\"https://mona.vn/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/dem-giang-sinh-la-ngay-nao-phan-biet-dem-24-va-ngay-25-12-202211140653279095.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-34476\" srcset=\"https://mona.vn/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/dem-giang-sinh-la-ngay-nao-phan-biet-dem-24-va-ngay-25-12-202211140653279095.jpg 800w, https://mona.vn/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/dem-giang-sinh-la-ngay-nao-phan-biet-dem-24-va-ngay-25-12-202211140653279095-768x432.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"></figure>\r\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center\"><em>T chc tic Ging sinh ti nh</em></p>\r\n<p>Ging sinh cng l dp nhng ngi thn trong gia nh, bn b on t, hp mt bn nn khng th thiu mt bui tic nho nh.&nbsp;<strong>Vo thi tit se lnh ca nhng ngy cui nm, nhng ngi thn yu ngi quay qun bn nhau v cng thng thc nhng mn n ngon th tht m cng phi khng no.</strong></p>\r\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" src=\"https://mona.vn/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/dem-giang-sinh-la-ngay-nao-phan-biet-dem-24-va-ngay-25-12-202211140653391616.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-34475\" srcset=\"https://mona.vn/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/dem-giang-sinh-la-ngay-nao-phan-biet-dem-24-va-ngay-25-12-202211140653391616.jpg 800w, https://mona.vn/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/dem-giang-sinh-la-ngay-nao-phan-biet-dem-24-va-ngay-25-12-202211140653391616-768x432.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"></figure>\r\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center\"><em>Tng thip Ging sinh</em></p>\r\n<p>Vo m Noel ngi ta thng tng nhau cho nhau nhng tm thip mang y tnh yu thng, bn trong thip l nhng tm t mun gi gm, nhng li chc nhau. Ngoi ra thit k ca thip ngy nay rt p v a dng, cng lm tn thm  ngha ca mn qu.</p>\r\n<p><em>Hy vng qua bi vit ny gip bn bit c m Ging Sinh l ngy no? Phn bit m 24/12 v ngy 25/12. Chc bn v gia nh c ma Ging Sinh vui v v m p.</em></p>\r\n</div>','m Ging Sinh l ngy no? Phn bit m 24 v ngy 25/12','','inherit','closed','closed','','9-revision-v1','','','2023-09-16 11:33:07','2023-09-16 11:33:07','',9,'http://localhost/mona/?p=10',0,'revision','',0),
