giay-dan-tuong-8.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"1730,1460\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"cach-chon-giay-dan-tuong (8)\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://kientrucgiacquan.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/cach-chon-giay-dan-tuong-8-300x253.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://kientrucgiacquan.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/cach-chon-giay-dan-tuong-8-1024x864.jpg\" data-lazy-loaded=\"1\"></a></p>\r\n<ol start=\"4\">\r\n<li><strong>Nhng lu  khc khi chn giy dn tng:</strong></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Cc mu giy dn tng c sc dc s lm trn nh cao hn hoc sc ngang s mang li cm gic phng rng hn v trn nh thp xung.</li>\r\n<li>Cc mu giy ha tit to khng nn dng cho nhng&nbsp;<strong>khng gian</strong>&nbsp;nh v n s khin chng c v nh hn.</li>\r\n<li>Mu ti c th lm cn phng trng nh hn. Ngc li, vi mu sng s lm cn phng trng to v rng hn.</li>\r\n<li>Bn cng nn ch  n hng ca ngi nh khi chn giy dn tng nh: i vi nhng ngi nh hng nng gt (nh Ty Nam, Ty) nn chn cc mu giy dn tng c mu nht, trnh phn quang  gim bt  chi. Nhng hng n nh sng mnh vi gc chiu sng cao (nh ng Nam, Nam) th c th dng giy dn tng c mu sm hn v a dng hn</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>Hy vng vi nhng chia s trn, Mona  gip bn c thm nhng kinh nghim  c th chn c nhng mu giy dn tng ph hp cho tng khng gian trong ngi nh mnh.</p>\r\n</div>','Cch chn giy dn tng cho tng khng gian trong nh bn','','inherit','closed','closed','','12-revision-v1','','','2023-09-16 11:35:00','2023-09-16 11:35:00','',12,'http://localhost/mona/?p=13',0,'revision','',0),
(14,1,'2023-09-16 11:35:42','2023-09-16 11:35:42','<div style=\"padding:10px\">\r\n<p><strong>1. NH NGHA.</strong></p>\r\n<p>Vt liu (VL)&nbsp;<i>composite</i>&nbsp;l vt liu t hp (mc  v m) ca hai hay nhiu vt liu thnh phn nhm to ra vt liu mi c tnh cht tri hn tnh cht ca tng vt liu thnh phn.</p>\r\n<p><span id=\"more-5313\"></span>V d:<br>\r\nSi thy tinh (bn, gin) + nha polyester (khng ha cht, cng gin) =&nbsp;<u>composite</u>&nbsp;(bn, khng ha cht, do dai).<br>\r\nPhn loi :<br>\r\nTheo hnh dng vt liu gia cng th c hai loi ch yu: si v ht.<br>\r\nTheo bn cht vt liu nn th c: nn hu c, kim loi, v nn gm.</p>\r\n<p><strong>2. LCH S<br>\r\n</strong></p>\r\n<p>Nhng vt liu compozit n gin  c t rt xa xa. Khong 5000 nm trc cng nguyn con ngi  bit trn nhng vin  nh vo t trc khi lm gch  trnh b cong vnh khi phi nng. V in hnh v compozit chnh l hp cht c dng  p xc ca ngi Ai Cp.</p>\r\n<p>Chnh thin nhin  to ra cu trc composite trc tin,  l thn cy g, c cu trc composite, gm nhiu sixenlulo di c kt ni vi nhau bng licnin. Kt qu ca s lin kt hi ho y l thn cy va bn v do- mt cu trc composite l tng.</p>\r\n<p>Ngi Hy Lp c cng  bit ly mt ong trn vi t, , ct si lm vt liu xy dng. V  Vit Nam, ngy xa truyn li cch lm nh bng bn trn vi rm bm nh  trt vch nh, khi kh to ra lp vt liu cng, mt v ma h v m vo ma ng</p>\r\n<p>Mc d composite l vt liu  c t lu, nhng ngnh khoa hc v vt liu composite ch mi hnh thnh gn vi s xut hin trong cng ngh ch to tn la  M t nhng nm 1950. T  n nay, khoa hc cng ngh vt liu composite  pht trin trn ton th gii v c khi thut ng vt liu mi ng ngha vi vt liu composite.</p>\r\n<p><strong>3. THNH PHN V TNH CHT.</strong><a id=\"more804333\" name=\"more804333\"></a></p>\r\n<p><strong>3.1. THNH PHN.</strong></p>\r\n<p>Vt liu composite thng gm hai thnh phn chnh: VL nn v VL gia cng.<br>\r\nVL nn bao gm: polymer (polyester, PE, PP, PVC, Epoxy, cao su), kim loi, ceramic(xi mng)<br>\r\nVL gia cng: cc loi si (thy tinh, cellulose, cacbon, acramic), ht (ht kim loi, ht t st, bt g, bt ), hoc cc hnh dng c bit khc.</p>\r\n<p>Vai tr v tnh cht ca cc VL thnh phn:</p>\r\n<p><strong>Vt liu nn</strong></p>\r\n<p>-L cht kt dnh v to mi trng phn tn.<br>\r\n-Truyn ng sut sang pha gia cng khi c ngoi lc tc dng.<br>\r\n-Bo v pha gia cng khng b h hng do tn cng ca mi trng.<br>\r\n-Bn do dai (chng li s pht trin ca vt nt)<br>\r\n-Ngoi ra cn ng gp cc tnh cht cn thit khc nh: cch in,  do dai, mu sc.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Vt liu gia cng</strong></p>\r\n<p>-ng vai tr l im chu ng sut tp trung.<br>\r\n-Tnh khng ha cht mi trng v nhit .<br>\r\n-Phn tn tt vo VL nn.<br>\r\n-Thun li cho qu trnh gia cng.<br>\r\n-Truyn nhit v gii nhit tt.<br>\r\n-Thn thin vi mi trng.<br>\r\n-H thp gi thnh m em lai tnh cht vt tri.</p>\r\n<p><strong>3.2. TNH CHT CHUNG CA VT LIU COMPOSITE.</strong></p>\r\n<p> Khi lng ring b do vy tnh nng c l ring cao hn thp v cc VL truyn thng khc (thy tinh, gm, g..) rt nhiu.<br>\r\n Chu mi trng, khng ha cht cao, khng tn km trong bo qun v chng n mn, khng cn sn bo qun nh VL kim loi , g<br>\r\n Cch in v cch nhit tt.<br>\r\n Bn lu hn (thi gian s dng ko di.)<br>\r\n Gia cng ch to n gin, nhanh, a dng, d to hnh, thay i v sa cha d.<br>\r\n Chi ph u t thp.<br>\r\n Gi thnh khng cao m tnh cht vt tri.</p>\r\n<p><strong>4. NG DNG.</strong></p>\r\n<p>T cc tnh cht hp dn ca n m VL composite c rt nhiu ng dng. Vt liu composite l vt liu ca ngy mai, n ang thay th dn hu ht cc loi vt liu truyn thng: kim loi, g, gm s.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Mt s sn phm t vt liu composite</strong></p>\r\n<p> trang tr ni tht</p>\r\n<p>V ng c tn la</p>\r\n<p>V tn la, my bay, tu v tr</p>\r\n<p>Bnh chu p lc cao.</p>\r\n<p>ng dn xng du composite cao cp 3 lp (S dng cng ngh cun t ca Nga v cc tiu chun sn xut ng dn xng, du).</p>\r\n<p>ng dn nc sch, nc th, nc ngun composite (hay cn gi l ng nha ct si thy tinh);</p>\r\n<p>ng dn nc thi, dn ha cht composite;</p>\r\n<p>ng thy nng, ng dn nc ngun qua vng nc ngm mn, nhim phn;</p>\r\n<p>V bc cc loi bn b, thng cha hng, mt bn gh, trang tr ni tht, tm panell composite;</p>\r\n<p>H thng ng thot rc nh cao tng;</p>\r\n<p>H thng s cch in, s polymer, s cilicon, s epoxy cc loi s chui, s , s cu giao, s trong cc b thit b in, chng st, cu ch;</p>\r\n<p>Lp xe  t, xe my, xe p;</p>\r\n<p>V tu thuyn composite (v li)..</p>\r\n<p>Thng rc cng cng</p>\r\n<p>M hnh  chi tr em</p>\r\n</div>','Cht liu Composite l g ?','','publish','open','open','','chat-lieu-composite-la-gi','','','2023-09-16 11:35:42','2023-09-16 11:35:42','',0,'http://localhost/mona/?p=14',0,'post','',0),
